trans-unit.source: Generates classes for Web services that use the SOAP protocol.
trans-unit.target: Genererar klasser för webbtjänster som använder SOAP-protokoll.

trans-unit.source: The SoapProtocolImporter class generates client proxy code or abstract server code according to the SOAP protocol.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SoapProtocolImporter genererar klientkod proxy eller abstrakt serverkoden enligt SOAP-protokoll.

trans-unit.source: The class generates a class for each supported binding defined in a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document.
trans-unit.target: Klassen genererar en klass för varje bindning som stöds och som definieras i ett dokument för Web Services WSDL (Description Language).

trans-unit.source: Typically, instead of invoking SoapProtocolImporter directly, a developer uses the class indirectly through the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> class.
trans-unit.target: Normalt använder en utvecklare i stället för att anropa SoapProtocolImporter direkt klassen indirekt via <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>klass.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the generation of a binding class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar generering av en bindning-klass.

trans-unit.source: During generation of a class for a given binding, the BeginClass method executes before the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter> class generates methods that correspond to operations.
trans-unit.target: Under genereringen av en klass för en given bindning metoden BeginClass körs innan den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>klassen genererar metoder som motsvarar operations.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>

trans-unit.source: A binding class.
trans-unit.target: En bindning-klass.

trans-unit.source: Performs initialization for an entire code namespace during code generation.
trans-unit.target: Utför initieringen av ett namnområde för hela koden under kodgenerering.

trans-unit.source: During code generation, the BeginNamespace method executes before the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter> class generates classes that represent bindings.
trans-unit.target: Under kodgenerering av metoden BeginNamespace körs innan den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>klassen genererar klasser som representerar bindningar.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>

trans-unit.source: Processes a binding class after the generation of methods.
trans-unit.target: Bearbetar en klass för bindning efter generering av metoder.

trans-unit.source: During generation of a class for a given binding, the EndClass method executes after the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter> class generates methods that correspond to operations.
trans-unit.target: Under genereringen av en klass för en given bindning metoden EndClass körs efter den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>klassen genererar metoder som motsvarar operations.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>

trans-unit.source: Performs processing for an entire code namespace after binding class generation.
trans-unit.target: Utför bearbetning av ett namnområde för hela koden efter klass generation.

trans-unit.source: During code generation, the EndNamespace method executes after the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter> class generates classes that represent bindings.
trans-unit.target: Under kodgenerering av metoden EndNamespace körs efter den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>klassen genererar klasser som representerar bindningar.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>

trans-unit.source: Generates method code for a binding class.
trans-unit.target: Genererar koden för en bindning-klass.

trans-unit.source: During generation of a class for a given binding, the GenerateMethod method executes for each binding class method that represents an operation.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GenerateMethod körs för varje metod för binding klass som representerar en åtgärd under genereringen av en klass för en given bindning.

trans-unit.source: The method code for a binding class.
trans-unit.target: Metoden koden för en bindning-klass.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether a class can be generated for the current binding.
trans-unit.target: Anger om en klass kan skapas för den aktuella bindningen.

trans-unit.source: The IsBindingSupported method determines whether to generate a class for the current binding, as represented by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IsBindingSupported avgör om du vill skapa en klass för den aktuella bindningen som representeras av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A>

trans-unit.source: The method checks whether the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A> property's <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding.Extensions%2A> property contains a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding> instance.
trans-unit.target: Metoden kontrollerar om den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A>egenskapens <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding.Extensions%2A>-egenskapen innehåller en <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding>instans.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding.Extensions%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A>

trans-unit.source: In addition, the transport mechanism obtained through the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding.Transport%2A> property must be supported by the current Web services configuration.
trans-unit.target: Dessutom kan transportmekanismen erhållits via den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding.Transport%2A>egenskapen måste stödjas av den aktuella konfigurationen för Web services.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding.Transport%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the class can be generated for the current binding; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om klassen kan skapas för den aktuella bindningen; Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the current operation's operation flow is supported.
trans-unit.target: Anger om den aktuella åtgärden åtgärden flödet stöds.

trans-unit.source: The IsOperationFlowSupported method determines whether to generate a method for the current operation, as represented by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IsOperationFlowSupported avgör om du vill skapa en metod för den aktuella åtgärden som representeras av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation>

trans-unit.source: This evaluation takes place for each operation in a binding for which a class is being generated.
trans-unit.target: Utvärderingen sker för varje åtgärd i en bindning som en klass genereras.

trans-unit.source: If a `false` value is returned, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.UnsupportedOperationWarning%2A> method executes.
trans-unit.target: Om en `false` värde returneras den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.UnsupportedOperationWarning%2A>metoden Kör.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.UnsupportedOperationWarning%2A>

trans-unit.source: A `true` value is returned only if the input value is <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow>.
trans-unit.target: En `true` värde returneras bara om indatavärdet är <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow>eller <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection.Flow%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection.Flow%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection.Flow%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A> property is of type <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A>Egenskapen är av typen <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow"></xref> enumeration value that represents a transmission pattern.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow"> </xref> -värde som representerar ett mönster för överföring.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the current operation's operation flow is supported; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om den aktuella åtgärden åtgärden flödet stöds. Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Checks for the presence of "http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/" in a string that represents a list of Uniform Resource Indicators (URIs).
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerar förekomsten av "http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/" i en sträng som representerar en lista över Uniform Resource indikatorer (URI: er).

trans-unit.source: A space-delimited list of URIs.
trans-unit.target: En mellanslags-avgränsad lista med URI: er.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value of "Soap".

trans-unit.source: Gets the object of type <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.SoapCodeExporter"></xref> used internally by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter"></xref> class to generate code from mappings between SOAP-encoded XML schema content and .NET Framework types.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar objekt av typen <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.SoapCodeExporter"> </xref> används internt i den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter"> </xref> klassen om du vill skapa kod från mappningar mellan SOAP-kodad XML schema innehåll och .NET Framework-typer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter> class uses a <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.SoapCodeExporter> object to create code from .NET Framework type mappings for XML schema elements and data types that enable SOAP encoding, as opposed to literal XML Schema usage.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>klassen använder en <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.SoapCodeExporter>objekt att skapa kod från .NET Framework mappningar av datatyper för XML-schema element och datatyper som möjliggör SOAP-kodning, till skillnad från literal användning av XML-schemat.</xref:System.Xml.Serialization.SoapCodeExporter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>

trans-unit.source: SOAP encoding is specified in section 5 of the SOAP 1.1 specification.
trans-unit.target: SOAP-kodning anges i avsnittet 5 i SOAP 1.1-specifikationen.

trans-unit.source: SOAP encoding uses the namespace "http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/".
trans-unit.target: SOAP-kodning använder namnområdet "http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/".
